# Functional Consulting & Business Analysis Portfolio

Welcome! This repository showcases a curated selection of digital transformation frameworks, functional specifications, and data-mapping architectures designed to bridge the gap between complex business requirements and technical execution.

Each project folder contains sanitized, enterprise-ready artifacts—including Mermaid.js interactive workflows, API data schemas, and user stories—representing real-world solutions built to drive operational velocity.

